@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_iheass(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.sin(v1)
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.11)) - ((v0 + 0.09 - tmp + 0.82) * 0.13))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = 0.69
    v2 = (wp.abs((v0 + 0.34 - v1 + 0.59)) * ((v2 + 0.07 + v1 + 0.28) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.24)))
    tmp = v0
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.sin(v0 + 0.40)) / ((tmp + 0.14 - v1 + 0.28) + (tmp + 0.81 + v0 + 0.05)))
    data[tid] = v0
